MLA distributes footwearPendurti MLA Bandaru Satyanarayana Murthy on Friday gave away gum shoes to members of Subhrata Mutually-Aided Rag Pickers Labour Contract Co-operative Society Limited in the Janmabhoomi programme at Ekalavya Colony.Society CEO Pragada Vasu and Zone Commissioner Sivaji participated.Training programmein meditationInstitute of Sri Ramachandra Consciousness will organise a free training programme in meditation on Saturday and Sunday at Quarter No. 324/B, Sector V of Steel Plant Quarters, Ukkunagaram.Those interested and aged between 18 and 55 years may contact Y. Narayana Murthy on phone number 8500094810.